us-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-12 px-7 py-3 text-base\" href=\"/egitimler\">Eğitimleri İncele<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"sacred-frame relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-white/70 bg-card/70 p-3 shadow-soft\"><img alt=\"Gönül İlhan için premium portre yer tutucusu\" width=\"880\" height=\"980\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"aspect-[0.9] w-full rounded-[1.5rem] object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgonul-ilhan-portrait.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgonul-ilhan-portrait.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgonul-ilhan-portrait.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/55 bg-ivory/84 p-4 shadow-soft backdrop-blur sm:bottom-7 sm:left-7 sm:right-7 sm:p-5\"><p class=\"text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-gold sm:text-xs sm:tracking-[0.22em]\">Kişisel harita · Döngüler · Eğitim</p><p class=\"mt-2 font-editorial text-xl leading-tight text-navy sm:text-2xl\">Sakin, etik ve içgörü odaklı numeroloji yaklaşımı.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"container py-10 sm:py-12\"><div class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur h-full\"><div class=\"min-w-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 space-y-3 p-5\"><p class=\"font-editorial text-4xl text-navy\">1:1</p><h2 class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">Bireysel danışmanlıklar</h2><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground\">Kişisel harita ve dönem farkındalığına odaklanan özel seanslar.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur h-full\"><div class=\"min-w-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 space-y-3 p-5\"><p class=\"font-editorial text-4xl text-navy\">4+</p><h2 class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">Eğitim programları</h2><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground\">Temelden uygulamaya uzanan numeroloji eğitim akışı.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur h-full\"><div class=\"min-w-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 space-y-3 p-5\"><p class=\"font-editorial text-4xl text-navy\">Online</p><h2 class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">Seans imkânı</h2><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground\">Türkiye ve yurt dışından katılım için esnek görüşme seçeneği.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur h-full\"><div class=\"min-w-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 space-y-3 p-5\"><p class=\"font-editorial text-4xl text-navy\">4.9</p><h2 class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">Katılımcı yorumları</h2><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground\">Sade, anlaşılır ve güvenli alan hissiyle aktarılan deneyimler.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"container grid gap-10 py-14 sm:py-16 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr] lg:items-center\"><div class=\"relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-white/80 bg-card p-3 shadow-soft\"><img alt=\"Numeroloji seansı için defter, sayılar ve sıcak ışık kompozisyonu\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"920\" height=\"720\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"aspect-[1.18] w-full rounded-[1.5rem] object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-numerology.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-numerology.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-numerology.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><div class=\"space-y-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-4\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Gönül İlhan</span><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2rem] leading-[1.1] text-navy sm:text-5xl sm:leading-[1.08]\">Sayıları kader cümlesi değil, içgörü dili olarak okuyan bir yaklaşım.</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg sm:leading-8\">Gönül İlhan, numerolojiyi kişisel gelişim yolculuğunda anlamlı sorular sormaya yardımcı olan zarif bir farkındalık yöntemi olarak sunar.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-border/70 bg-card/70 p-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-feather mb-4 h-5 w-5 text-gold\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12.67 19a2 2 0 0 0 1.416-.588l6.154-6.172a6 6 0 0 0-8.49-8.49L5.586 9.914A2 2 0 0 0 5 11.328V18a1 1 0 0 0 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"M16 8 2 22\"></path><path d=\"M17.5 15H9\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">Kişisel farkındalık odağı</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground\">Gönül İlhan, numerolojiyi kişinin kendisiyle daha dürüst ve şefkatli bir ilişki kurmasına yardımcı olan sembolik bir dil olarak ele alır.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-border/70 bg-card/70 p-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-feather mb-4 h-5 w-5 text-gold\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12.67 19a2 2 0 0 0 1.416-.588l6.154-6.172a6 6 0 0 0-8.49-8.49L5.586 9.914A2 2 0 0 0 5 11.328V18a1 1 0 0 0 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"M16 8 2 22\"></path><path d=\"M17.5 15H9\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">Eğitim ve danışmanlık dili</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground\">Seans ve eğitimlerinde karmaşık kavramları sadeleştirir; katılımcının kendi içgörüsünü güçlendirmeyi merkeze alır.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-border/70 bg-card/70 p-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-feather mb-4 h-5 w-5 text-gold\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12.67 19a2 2 0 0 0 1.416-.588l6.154-6.172a6 6 0 0 0-8.49-8.49L5.586 9.914A2 2 0 0 0 5 11.328V18a1 1 0 0 0 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"M16 8 2 22\"></path><path d=\"M17.5 15H9\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">Güvenli iletişim alanı</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground\">Her çalışma, kesin yargılar yerine anlamaya, dinlemeye ve kişinin özgür iradesini desteklemeye odaklanır.</p></div></div><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2\" href=\"/gonul-ilhan\">Gönül İlhan&#x27;ı Tanı<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></section><section class=\"bg-white/34 py-14 sm:py-16\"><div class=\"container space-y-10\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-4\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Hizmetler</span><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2rem] leading-[1.1] text-navy sm:text-5xl sm:leading-[1.08]\">Bireysel seanslardan grup atölyelerine, ihtiyacına göre şekillenen çalışmalar.</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg sm:leading-8\">Her çalışma, kesin yargılar yerine farkındalık ve sorumluluk alanını büyütmeyi hedefler.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group h-full transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-gold/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 space-y-2 p-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"mb-2 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gold-sheen text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg></span><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\">Bireysel Numeroloji Danışmanlığı</h3></div><div class=\"min-w-0 p-5 pt-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 space-y-5\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Doğum tarihi ve isim titreşimleri üzerinden kişisel potansiyel, güçlü yönler ve dönemsel temalar üzerine farkındalık seansı.</p><div class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm text-navy\"><p><span class=\"font-semibold\">Süre:</span> <!-- -->75 dakika</p><p><span class=\"font-semibold\">Format:</span> <!-- -->Online veya yüz yüze</p></div><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2 w-full\" href=\"/randevu\">Randevu Al<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group h-full transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-gold/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 space-y-2 p-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"mb-2 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gold-sheen text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart-handshake h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z\"></path><path d=\"M12 5 9.04 7.96a2.17 2.17 0 0 0 0 3.08c.82.82 2.13.85 3 .07l2.07-1.9a2.82 2.82 0 0 1 3.79 0l2.96 2.66\"></path><path d=\"m18 15-2-2\"></path><path d=\"m15 18-2-2\"></path></svg></span><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\">İlişki ve Uyum Analizi</h3></div><div class=\"min-w-0 p-5 pt-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 space-y-5\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">İlişki dinamiklerini, iletişim ritimlerini ve tamamlayıcı yönleri daha bilinçli görmeye yardımcı olan özel analiz.</p><div class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm text-navy\"><p><span class=\"font-semibold\">Süre:</span> <!-- -->90 dakika</p><p><span class=\"font-semibold\">Format:</span> <!-- -->Online veya yüz yüze</p></div><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2 w-full\" href=\"/randevu\">Randevu Al<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group h-full transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-gold/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 space-y-2 p-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"mb-2 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gold-sheen text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg></span><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\">Kişisel Yıl ve Döngü Danışmanlığı</h3></div><div class=\"min-w-0 p-5 pt-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 space-y-5\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">İçinde bulunulan yılın numerolojik temasını, destekleyici karar alanlarını ve ritmini anlamaya yönelik seans.</p><div class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm text-navy\"><p><span class=\"font-semibold\">Süre:</span> <!-- -->60 dakika</p><p><span class=\"font-semibold\">Format:</span> <!-- -->Online</p></div><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2 w-full\" href=\"/randevu\">Randevu Al<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group h-full transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-gold/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 space-y-2 p-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"mb-2 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gold-sheen text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users-round h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 21a8 8 0 0 0-16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"10\" cy=\"8\" r=\"5\"></circle><path d=\"M22 20c0-3.37-2-6.5-4-8a5 5 0 0 0-.45-8.3\"></path></svg></span><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\">Kurumsal / Grup Atölyeleri</h3></div><div class=\"min-w-0 p-5 pt-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 space-y-5\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Ekip içi farkındalık, iletişim ve kişisel gelişim odağında hazırlanan numeroloji temelli atölyeler.</p><div class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm text-navy\"><p><span class=\"font-semibold\">Süre:</span> <!-- -->2-3 saat veya özel program</p><p><span class=\"font-semibold\">Format:</span> <!-- -->Online, yüz yüze veya hibrit</p></div><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2 w-full\" href=\"/randevu\">Randevu Al<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"container space-y-10 py-14 sm:py-16\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-6 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-4\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Eğitimler</span><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2rem] leading-[1.1] text-navy sm:text-5xl sm:leading-[1.08]\">Numerolojiyi öğrenmek isteyenler için özenle yapılandırılmış programlar.</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg sm:leading-8\">Temelden ileri seviyeye uzanan eğitimler; etik yorumlama, uygulama ve kişisel farkındalık odağıyla tasarlandı.</p></div><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2 w-full sm:w-fit\" href=\"/egitimler\">Tüm Eğitimler<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group flex h-full flex-col transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-rose/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 space-y-2 p-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy w-fit\">Başlangıç</span><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\">Numerolojiye Giriş Eğitimi</h3></div><div class=\"min-w-0 p-5 pt-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 flex flex-1 flex-col gap-5\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Sayıların sembolik dilini öğrenmek ve kendi haritanı temel seviyede okumaya başlamak isteyenler için zarif bir başlangıç.</p><div class=\"grid gap-3 text-sm text-navy\"><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg>4 hafta</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-monitor mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"8\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"21\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"17\" y2=\"21\"></line></svg>Canlı online</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-signal mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><path d=\"M2 20h.01\"></path><path d=\"M7 20v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v-8\"></path><path d=\"M17 20V8\"></path><path d=\"M22 4v16\"></path></svg>Numerolojiyle ilk kez tanışanlar, kişisel farkındalık çalışmalarına yeni bir araç eklemek isteyenler.</span></div><div class=\"mt-auto\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2 w-full\" href=\"/egitimler/numerolojiye-giris-egitimi\">Eğitim Detaylarını Gör<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group flex h-full flex-col transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-rose/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 space-y-2 p-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy w-fit\">İleri</span><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\">İleri Seviye Numeroloji Eğitimi</h3></div><div class=\"min-w-0 p-5 pt-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 flex flex-1 flex-col gap-5\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Temel bilgisi olan katılımcılar için yorumlama derinliği, harita sentezi ve danışmanlık dili odaklı program.</p><div class=\"grid gap-3 text-sm text-navy\"><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg>8 hafta</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-monitor mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"8\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"21\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"17\" y2=\"21\"></line></svg>Canlı online + uygulama</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-signal mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><path d=\"M2 20h.01\"></path><path d=\"M7 20v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v-8\"></path><path d=\"M17 20V8\"></path><path d=\"M22 4v16\"></path></svg>Temel numeroloji bilgisine sahip, harita okuma becerisini derinleştirmek isteyen katılımcılar.</span></div><div class=\"mt-auto\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2 w-full\" href=\"/egitimler/ileri-seviye-numeroloji-egitimi\">Eğitim Detaylarını Gör<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group flex h-full flex-col transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-rose/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 space-y-2 p-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy w-fit\">Tüm seviyeler</span><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\">Kişisel Harita Okuma Atölyesi</h3></div><div class=\"min-w-0 p-5 pt-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 flex flex-1 flex-col gap-5\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Kendi doğum tarihi ve isim titreşimlerinle çalışarak haritanı rehber eşliğinde keşfedeceğin yoğun atölye.</p><div class=\"grid gap-3 text-sm text-navy\"><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg>1 gün</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-monitor mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"8\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"21\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"17\" y2=\"21\"></line></svg>Online veya yüz yüze</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-signal mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><path d=\"M2 20h.01\"></path><path d=\"M7 20v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v-8\"></path><path d=\"M17 20V8\"></path><path d=\"M22 4v16\"></path></svg>Kendi haritası üzerinde çalışarak öğrenmek isteyen, deneyim odaklı katılımcılar.</span></div><div class=\"mt-auto\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2 w-full\" href=\"/egitimler/kisisel-harita-okuma-atolyesi\">Eğitim Detaylarını Gör<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group flex h-full flex-col transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-rose/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 space-y-2 p-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy w-fit\">Orta / İleri</span><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\">Uygulamalı Numeroloji Programı</h3></div><div class=\"min-w-0 p-5 pt-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 flex flex-1 flex-col gap-5\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Harita okuma pratiğini artırmak, soru-cevap alanı açmak ve danışmanlık becerisini geliştirmek isteyenler için uygulama programı.</p><div class=\"grid gap-3 text-sm text-navy\"><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg>6 hafta</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-monitor mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"8\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"21\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"17\" y2=\"21\"></line></svg>Küçük grup</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-signal mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><path d=\"M2 20h.01\"></path><path d=\"M7 20v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v-8\"></path><path d=\"M17 20V8\"></path><path d=\"M22 4v16\"></path></svg>Numerolojiyi öğrenmiş fakat daha fazla pratik, geri bildirim ve yorumlama özgüveni isteyenler.</span></div><div class=\"mt-auto\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2 w-full\" href=\"/egitimler/uygulamali-numeroloji-programi\">Eğitim Detaylarını Gör<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"container py-14 sm:py-16\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border shadow-soft backdrop-blur overflow-hidden border-gold/35 bg-navy text-primary-foreground\"><div class=\"min-w-0 grid gap-6 p-4 min-[390px]:p-6 sm:gap-8 sm:p-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.72fr_1fr] lg:p-10\"><div class=\"sacred-frame flex min-h-52 flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-[1.8rem] bg-white/7 p-5 text-center sm:min-h-64 sm:p-8\"><p class=\"mb-4 inline-flex max-w-full flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-champagne/30 px-3 py-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-champagne sm:tracking-[0.2em]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-3.5 w-3.5\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg>25.05.2026</p><p class=\"text-sm text-primary-foreground/70\">Günün Sayısı</p><p class=\"font-editorial text-7xl leading-none text-champagne sm:text-8xl\">4</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-xs text-primary-foreground/56\">Rakamların toplamı: <!-- -->22</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center space-y-5\"><div class=\"inline-flex w-fit max-w-full flex-wrap items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-champagne/24 bg-white/6 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-champagne\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg>Bugünün sembolik teması</div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-3xl leading-tight sm:text-5xl\">Düzen ve Temel</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-8 text-primary-foreground/78\">Bugün sadeleşmek, plan yapmak ve güven veren yapılar kurmak için destekleyici olabilir.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-champagne/20 bg-white/6 p-5\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-champagne\">Günlük öneri</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-primary-foreground/76\">Dağınık kalan bir alanı, dosyayı veya gündem başlığını düzenle.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 shadow-glow hover:-translate-y-0.5 min-h-11 px-6 py-2 w-full bg-champagne text-navy hover:bg-linen sm:w-auto\" href=\"/randevu\">Bugünün enerjisini daha derin keşfetmek için randevu al</a><p class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-xs leading-5 text-primary-foreground/58\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info mt-0.5 h-3.5 w-3.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg>Bu yorum kişisel farkındalık ve ilham amaçlıdır.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white/34 py-14 sm:py-16\"><div class=\"container space-y-10\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-4\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Yorumlar</span><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2rem] leading-[1.1] text-navy sm:text-5xl sm:leading-[1.08]\">Danışan ve katılımcı deneyimlerinden sakin notlar.</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg sm:leading-8\">Yorumlar temsilidir; gerçek yayında izin alınmış danışan geri bildirimleriyle değiştirilebilir.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur h-full\"><div class=\"min-w-0 space-y-5 p-5 sm:p-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Bireysel Danışmanlık</span><div class=\"flex items-center gap-0.5 text-gold\" aria-label=\"5 yıldız\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star h-4 w-4 fill-current\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star h-4 w-4 fill-current\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star h-4 w-4 fill-current\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star h-4 w-4 fill-current\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star h-4 w-4 fill-current\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg></div></div><blockquote class=\"text-base leading-8 text-navy\">“<!-- -->Seans boyunca kendimi yargılanmadan dinlenmiş hissettim. Haritamdaki temalar günlük hayatımla çok sade ve anlamlı biçimde ilişkilendirildi.<!-- -->”</blockquote><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">Aylin K.</p><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Bireysel danışmanlık katılımcısı</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur h-full\"><div class=\"min-w-0 space-y-5 p-5 sm:p-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Eğitim</span><div class=\"flex items-center gap-0.5 text-gold\" aria-label=\"5 yıldız\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star h-4 w-4 fill-current\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.