=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star h-4 w-4 fill-current\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg></div></div><blockquote class=\"text-base leading-8 text-navy\">“<!-- -->Atölye hem içten hem de çok iyi yapılandırılmıştı. Kendi haritam üzerinde çalışmak güçlü bir farkındalık alanı açtı.<!-- -->”</blockquote><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">Selin A.</p><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Harita okuma atölyesi</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"container space-y-10 py-14 sm:py-16\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-4\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Randevu Süreci</span><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2rem] leading-[1.1] text-navy sm:text-5xl sm:leading-[1.08]\">Net, sade ve güven veren bir iletişim akışı.</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg sm:leading-8\">Randevu talebinden seans veya eğitim başlangıcına kadar her adım anlaşılır şekilde ilerler.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur h-full\"><div class=\"min-w-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 p-6\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gold-sheen text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon-star h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 3a6 6 0 0 0 9 9 9 9 0 1 1-9-9\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"font-editorial text-4xl text-border\">0<!-- -->1</span></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-navy\">Hizmeti seç</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Bireysel danışmanlık, eğitim veya atölye seçeneklerinden ihtiyacına uygun olanı belirle.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur h-full\"><div class=\"min-w-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 p-6\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gold-sheen text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-messages-square h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14 9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6l-4 4V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M18 9h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v11l-4-4h-6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-1\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"font-editorial text-4xl text-border\">0<!-- -->2</span></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-navy\">Formu doldur</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Randevu sayfasından uygun tarih, saat ve görüşme tercihlerini güvenle ilet.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur h-full\"><div class=\"min-w-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 p-6\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gold-sheen text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart-handshake h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z\"></path><path d=\"M12 5 9.04 7.96a2.17 2.17 0 0 0 0 3.08c.82.82 2.13.85 3 .07l2.07-1.9a2.82 2.82 0 0 1 3.79 0l2.96 2.66\"></path><path d=\"m18 15-2-2\"></path><path d=\"m15 18-2-2\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"font-editorial text-4xl text-border\">0<!-- -->3</span></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-navy\">Ön görüşme / onay</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Talebin değerlendirilir, uygunluk ve detaylar kısa bir iletişimle netleştirilir.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur h-full\"><div class=\"min-w-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 p-6\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gold-sheen text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"font-editorial text-4xl text-border\">0<!-- -->4</span></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-navy\">Seans veya eğitim</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Sakin, yapılandırılmış ve kişisel sınırlarına saygılı bir çalışma alanı açılır.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"container grid gap-10 py-14 sm:py-16 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:items-start\"><div class=\"space-y-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-4\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Yazılar</span><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2rem] leading-[1.1] text-navy sm:text-5xl sm:leading-[1.08]\">Numerolojiye sakin ve gerçekçi bir bakış.</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg sm:leading-8\">Kısa yazılar; sayıların sembolik dilini, döngüleri ve eğitim sürecini daha anlaşılır kılmak için hazırlandı.</p></div><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 shadow-soft backdrop-blur bg-navy text-primary-foreground\"><div class=\"min-w-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 space-y-4 p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check h-8 w-8 text-champagne\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-editorial text-3xl\">Farkındalık amaçlı içerik</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-primary-foreground/72\">Yazılarda yer alan bilgiler, kişisel düşünme ve ilham alanı açmak içindir. Profesyonel sağlık, hukuk veya finans danışmanlığı yerine geçmez.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group h-full transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-gold/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 flex h-full flex-col gap-5 p-5 sm:p-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Numeroloji Temelleri</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-3.5 w-3.5\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg>12 Mayıs 2026</span><span class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">4 dk</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\"><a class=\"hover:text-gold\" href=\"/yazilar/numeroloji-nedir\">Numeroloji Nedir?</a></h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Numerolojiyi kehanet değil, sayıların sembolik dili üzerinden kişisel farkındalık geliştiren bir bakış açısı olarak ele alalım.</p></div><a class=\"mt-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-navy transition hover:text-gold\" href=\"/yazilar/numeroloji-nedir\">Yazıyı Oku<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group h-full transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-gold/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 flex h-full flex-col gap-5 p-5 sm:p-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Döngüler</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-3.5 w-3.5\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg>8 Mayıs 2026</span><span class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">5 dk</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\"><a class=\"hover:text-gold\" href=\"/yazilar/kisisel-yil-dongusu-ne-anlama-gelir\">Kişisel Yıl Döngüsü Ne Anlama Gelir?</a></h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Her yılın farklı bir teması olabilir. Kişisel yıl döngüsü, içinde bulunduğun döneme daha bilinçli bakmana yardımcı olur.</p></div><a class=\"mt-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-navy transition hover:text-gold\" href=\"/yazilar/kisisel-yil-dongusu-ne-anlama-gelir\">Yazıyı Oku<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group h-full transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-gold/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 flex h-full flex-col gap-5 p-5 sm:p-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Eğitim</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-3.5 w-3.5\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg>2 Mayıs 2026</span><span class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">3 dk</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\"><a class=\"hover:text-gold\" href=\"/yazilar/numeroloji-egitimine-kimler-katilabilir\">Numeroloji Eğitimine Kimler Katılabilir?</a></h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Numeroloji eğitimi yalnızca danışman olmak isteyenler için değil, kendini tanıma yolculuğunu derinleştirmek isteyen herkes için uygun olabilir.</p></div><a class=\"mt-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-navy transition hover:text-gold\" href=\"/yazilar/numeroloji-egitimine-kimler-katilabilir\">Yazıyı Oku<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group h-full transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-gold/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 flex h-full flex-col gap-5 p-5 sm:p-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Kişisel Gelişim</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-3.5 w-3.5\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg>27 Nisan 2026</span><span class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">4 dk</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\"><a class=\"hover:text-gold\" href=\"/yazilar/sayilarin-kisisel-farkindaliktaki-rolu\">Sayıların Kişisel Farkındalıktaki Rolü</a></h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Sayılar, kişiliği dar kalıplara hapsetmek yerine davranışlarımızı ve seçimlerimizi gözlemlemek için sembolik ipuçları sunabilir.</p></div><a class=\"mt-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-navy transition hover:text-gold\" href=\"/yazilar/sayilarin-kisisel-farkindaliktaki-rolu\">Yazıyı Oku<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white/34 py-14 sm:py-16\"><div class=\"container grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.85fr_1.15fr]\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-4\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">SSS</span><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2rem] leading-[1.1] text-navy sm:text-5xl sm:leading-[1.08]\">Sık sorulan sorular.</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg sm:leading-8\">Danışmanlık ve eğitim sürecine başlamadan önce merak edebileceğin temel konular.</p></div><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur\"><div class=\"min-w-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 p-6\"><div class=\"w-full\" data-orientation=\"vertical\"><div data-state=\"closed\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" class=\"border-b border-border/80\"><h3 data-orientation=\"vertical\" data-state=\"closed\" class=\"flex\"><button type=\"button\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_2d9btb_\" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-state=\"closed\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" id=\"radix-_R_d9btb_\" class=\"flex flex-1 items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left text-base font-medium text-navy transition-all hover:text-gold [&amp;[data-state=open]&gt;svg]:rotate-180\" data-radix-collection-item=\"\">Numeroloji danışmanlığı nasıl ilerler?<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></h3><div data-state=\"closed\" id=\"radix-_R_2d9btb_\" hidden=\"\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"radix-_R_d9btb_\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" class=\"overflow-hidden text-sm text-muted-foreground data-[state=closed]:animate-accordion-up data-[state=open]:animate-accordion-down\" style=\"--radix-accordion-content-height:var(--radix-collapsible-content-height);--radix-accordion-content-width:var(--radix-collapsible-content-width)\"></div></div><div data-state=\"closed\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" class=\"border-b border-border/80\"><h3 data-orientation=\"vertical\" data-state=\"closed\" class=\"flex\"><button type=\"button\" aria-controls=