e=\"closed\" class=\"flex\"><button type=\"button\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_3d9btb_\" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-state=\"closed\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" id=\"radix-_R_1d9btb_\" class=\"flex flex-1 items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left text-base font-medium text-navy transition-all hover:text-gold [&amp;[data-state=open]&gt;svg]:rotate-180\" data-radix-collection-item=\"\">Seanslar terapi yerine geçer mi?<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></h3><div data-state=\"closed\" id=\"radix-_R_3d9btb_\" hidden=\"\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"radix-_R_1d9btb_\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" class=\"overflow-hidden text-sm text-muted-foreground data-[state=closed]:animate-accordion-up data-[state=open]:animate-accordion-down\" style=\"--radix-accordion-content-height:var(--radix-collapsible-content-height);--radix-accordion-content-width:var(--radix-collapsible-content-width)\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"container py-14 sm:py-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"sacred-frame overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] bg-navy-depth p-5 text-primary-foreground shadow-soft min-[390px]:p-6 sm:p-12 lg:p-14\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] lg:items-center\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-champagne sm:text-sm sm:tracking-[0.24em]\">Nazik bir başlangıç</p><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2rem] leading-tight sm:text-5xl\">Kendi yolculuğunu sayılarla keşfetmeye hazır mısın?</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-8 text-primary-foreground/76\">Bir seans, eğitim ya da atölye ile numerolojiyi hayatına sakin, etik ve ilham veren bir farkındal